2.0.5.name: wordpress/10centmail-subscription-management-and-analytics
2.0.5.description:
The 10CentMail Wordpress plugin provides subscription management and analytics data to the 10CentMail desktop application.

This plugin is required for 10CentMail to provide subscribe and unsubscribe functionality as well as open and click tracking to the application. Install this plugin on any public facing website that will be used as a central point of customer interaction.
